The Header screen allows input of the information found in the header of the
milestone chart.  It appears as soon as the F2(Text) key is pressed from the
Main Screen or the Format Menu or when F5(Header) is pressed from the
Milestone/Footnote screen.
To change the information in the fields, type the new information and it will
overwrite the old information.  The insert key can be pressed to insert
characters in the middle of a field.  What is displayed on the screen when any
function key or return key is pressed is what will be saved.

To obtain help for any of the following subjects,  press the function key next
to the desired subject.

 
        F2  Edit
 
 
 
        F6  Milestone/Footnote
 
        F8  Return to Previous Menu
 
        F10 Exit from Help

Press F8 to return to the last menu screen or F10 to leave the help mode
